data.description: Embrace a life of luxury and endless fun in this stunning single-story dream home! Imagine: Creating lasting memories with loved ones in the spacious open floor plan, featuring glistening hardwood floors that exude warmth and elegance. Unleashing your inner chef in the gourmet kitchen, ample counter space, and a cozy fireplace for chilly evenings. Cooling off in the refreshing pool on a hot day or basking poolside with a good book. Finding your private sanctuary in the master suite, boasting a huge walk-in closet and a spa-like bathroom with a walk-in shower and luxurious bathtub. Hosting game nights and movie marathons in the spacious family room with a fireplace. Keeping your vehicles pristine in the oversized 3-car garage. Enjoying the convenience of being close to a vibrant shopping center. Relaxing and unwinding in the clean and quiet neighborhood. Saving on energy bills with the home's solar energy system. Peace of mind with low homeowner association fees.
